[[Image:Anthoceros levis.jpg|right|thumb|160px|A hornwort]]
===Etymology===
From [[horn]] + Old English [[wort]] "plant", from the fact that the spores are produced in slender horn-shaped structures.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[bryophyte]] with a leafless [[thallus]] characterized by a dominant [[gametophyte]] stage of the life cycle and a [[sporophyte]] stage shaped like a [[horn]].

